@startuml
title State diagram for the Green Rides system

[*] --> Login

state "Login" as Login
state "View Journey Details" as ViewJourneyDetails
state "Driving Mode" as DrivingMode
state "Select Place to Eat" as SelectPlaceToEat
state "Order Food" as OrderFood
state "Accident" as Accident
state "Feedback" as Feedback
state "Final" as Final

Login --> ViewJourneyDetails : Select Destination
ViewJourneyDetails --> ViewJourneyDetails : View Details
ViewJourneyDetails --> DrivingMode : Activate Driving Mode
ViewJourneyDetails --> SelectPlaceToEat : Select Place to Eat

DrivingMode --> DrivingMode : Drive
DrivingMode --> Accident : Accident Occurs
Accident --> Accident : Inform Authorities
Accident --> Feedback : Provide Feedback

SelectPlaceToEat --> OrderFood : Place Order
OrderFood --> ViewJourneyDetails : Cancel Order

Feedback --> Final : Complete Feedback
Final --> [*]

@enduml
